Kamfanin ya yi la'akari da matsakaicin yawan masu sauraro a kan CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
A lokacin babu bayanai daga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka yi hakan, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
