Yanzu al'ada ce ta neman ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da al'ada a Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya shafi wannan sabon fasalin na aikin kwaikwayo na John English - wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da John English kuma an sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da fim din John English.
