Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar 2018 ta Ryder Cup, ta doke ta ta Amurka ta hanyar 16.5 da 10.5 a wasan karshe a Le Golf National, a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta ci nasara shida a kan Turai kuma ba ta taba cin kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da kambin bayan tawagar da Thomas Byrne ya jagoranci ta samu maki 14.5, wanda ya kamata ta yi wa Amurka.
Phil Michelson, dan wasan Amurka, wanda ya yi ƙoƙari ya lashe gasar a mafi yawan lokutan, ya jefa harbinsa na farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na Par-3, bayan da ya yi rashin nasara a gaban Francisco Molinar.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya, Molinari, ya yi nasara a duk zagaye na gasar, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka ci 5-0-0, tun lokacin da aka kirkiro tsarin gasar ta yanzu a 1979.
Dan wasan Denmark, Torbjörn Olsen, ya ci Jordan Spit, dan Amurka, da maki 5 da 4 a tawagar Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ya fi kowa daraja a duniya, ya ba da lambar yabo ta 2 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya yin wasan karshe na Ryder Cup.
Sergio Garcia, tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup na Spain, ya lashe gasar a tarihin Turai da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma yanzu ba zan iya daina ba.
Wannan shekara ce mai wuya.
Saboda haka, ina godiya cewa Thomas ya amince da ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin ciki sosai don na dawo da kofin.
Wannan aikin tawagar ne, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka wa, "in ji Garcia mai cike da motsin rai bayan nasarar da ta samu a Turai.
Ya ba da lambar yabo ga abokin aikinsa John Ram, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya lashe Tiger Woods na golf na Amurka 2 da 1 a wasa daya.
Rah mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari sosai da na yi nasara a kan Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon wannan mutumin.
Woods ya yi nasara a wasanni hudu da ya yi a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan adadi mai ban mamaki na daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14, ya fi Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya a mako guda don samun mai ba da shawara, ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finus, waɗanda suka buga golf mai girma a duk faɗin gasar.
Jim Furyk, kyaftin din Amurka bayan wasan da ya buga a tawagarsa ya ce, "Ina alfahari da wadannan yara, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wannan safiya, mun yi wa Turai ta'aziyya.
Mun halaka.
"Na yi farin ciki sosai da na yi farin ciki sosai".
Yana da kyawawan kyaftin.
'Yan wasan da suka buga wa wasan 12 sun yi kyau sosai.
Za mu sake rukuni, zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin gasar cin kofin Rider, kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftinansu.
Dole ne ku biya kuɗin ku.
Mun fi mu kyau".
Labari na Red Circuit: Ƙarƙashin hankali a Pinellas, Menati, da Sarasota
Rahotanni na kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Tsaro ta Florida sun nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan jan ragin a yankin Tampa Bay.
Hukumar kifi da namun daji ta ce, a cikin kananan hukumomi na Pinellas, Menatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da Collier, an yi amfani da takunkumin da ke nuna cewa an hana su yin taro.
Red spots suna yadawa a kusan mil 130 a bakin teku, daga Pinella ta arewa zuwa garin Leeds ta kudu.
Ana ganin wuraren da ke kusa da bakin teku a kusan mil 10 daga garin Hillsborough amma a wurare da yawa fiye da a makon da ya gabata.
Ana kuma ganin wannan motsi a garin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan taro a garin Pinellas ko gaɓar tekun, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a garin Hillsborough a gaɓar tekun, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a garin Menate, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a garin Sarasota ko gaɓar tekun, daga ƙananan zuwa matsakaitan taro a garin Charlotte, daga ƙananan taro a garin Lise ko gaɓar tekun, da kuma sanyi a cikin ƙarfe na ƙarfe.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni game da tashin hankali a cikin biranen Pinellas da Menate da Sarasota da Li'i da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani rahoto ba game da tashin hankali a cikin numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
